title: [SOLVED]820-00239 Liquid Damage no SSD
message: Hi Guys, I will start troubleshooting a new Touchbar 820-00239 that doesnt have SSD showing. Some corrosion near NAND chip and on J6100. J6100 is that like a jtag connector, we can remove it? How about J9600 "lifeboat" which also seems not to be in use?

title: [SOLVED]820-00239 Liquid Damage no SSD
message: OK guys i figured it out, the connector is a jumper and no power goes to the SSD without it, put it back and now I have a happy 820-00239, customer and myself.
